''See aso [[cuándo]]''
==Spanish==
===Pronunciation===
* /ˈkwando/

===Etymology===
Latin '''[[quando]]'''.

===Pronoun===
# ''(relative)'' [[When]].
#: ''Ven cuando estás listo.''
#: Come when you're ready.

===Usage===
This same word also functions as the interrogative pronoun ''when?,'' but in such case it is written with an accent mark to distinguish it from these senses: ''¿[[cuándo]]?''

